              was a first draft — component structure, data flow, error handling
              patterns. I kept it conservative: fewer abstractions, more
              readable code. The next engineer who touches it should feel
              relief, not dread.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="cs-outcome">
